      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      ** Warning fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    WFldNmXAr
     C                   PARM                    WMsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    WMsgDtXAr
      *
      ** Transaction Details OK inds
     C                   PARM                    OKFEBO
      *
      ** Deal info passed from calling programs
     C                   PARM                    Data
 
